reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I used one of the 2 chargers with my Samsung phone. The phone charged quickly. I thought I needed a long cord, and this 10 foot one is plenty long enough. So far, I suspect I could have gotten by with a 6 foot cord. This came well-packaged, maybe too well packaged. The box could have been a lot smaller for its contents. The price was very reasonable. I have only used this for a few days, but if it stays reliable, I would highly recommend it.
